snippet.title: F-5E REMASTERED | OUT NOW
snippet.description:
The DCS: F-5E Remastered module is now available! If you are an existing owner of the previous F-5E you can upgrade today for just $9.99 for three months, thereafter the upgrade price will be increased to $14.99. This comprehensive remaster brings a wealth of enhancements including an entirely new external model and cockpit. 

DCS e-shop: https://www.digitalcombatsimulator.com/en/shop/modules/tiger_remastered/
